&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;nqx1ua&quot; data-start=&quot;283&quot; data-end=&quot;410&quot;&gt;Define and evolve API strategies that support current consumers while anticipating future scale, growth, and extensibility.&lt;/li&gt;
